<note id="fs-idm229380256" class="os-teacher">
<title>Suggested Sequencing</title>
<para id="fs-idm220629840">Use this Narrative alongside <link document="m80605">The Transcontinental Railroad</link> Narrative to highlight the infrastructure innovations of the Gilded Age.</para>
